{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"stroke","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stroke","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/ja/docs/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG Attribute reference home</a></p>\n\n<p><code>stroke</code>属性は与えられた図形要素の外側に描画される色を定義します。<code>stroke</code>属性のデフォルト値は&nbsp;<strong>none</strong> です<strong>.</strong></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用可能な場所","title":"使用可能な場所","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">カテゴリ</th>\n   <td>プレゼンテーション属性</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">値</th>\n   <td>\n    <p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Content_type#paint\">&lt;paint&gt;</a>, <code>context-fill</code>, <code>context-stroke</code></p>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">アニメーション</th>\n   <td>可</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">標準文書</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/painting.html#StrokeProperty\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"svg_line","title":"SVG Line with stroke","isH3":true,"content":"<h4 id=\"例1_stroke_を使用した直線\">例1: stroke を使用した直線</h4>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>50<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>300<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>path</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">stroke</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>green<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">d</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>M5 20 1215 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"例1 stroke を使用した直線 sample\" id=\"frame_例1_stroke_を使用した直線\" width=\"300\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stroke/_sample_.%E4%BE%8B1_stroke_%E3%82%92%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E3%81%97%E3%81%9F%E7%9B%B4%E7%B7%9A.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n\n<h4 id=\"例2_黒丸の枠線として青い_stroke_を使用\">例2: 黒丸の枠線として青い stroke を使用</h4>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code>​​<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>circle</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">cx</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>50<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">cy</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>50<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">r</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>40<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">stroke</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">stroke-width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">fill</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>black<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"例2 黒丸の枠線として青い stroke を使用 sample\" id=\"frame_例2_黒丸の枠線として青い_stroke_を使用\" width=\"100\" height=\"120\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stroke/_sample_.%E4%BE%8B2_%E9%BB%92%E4%B8%B8%E3%81%AE%E6%9E%A0%E7%B7%9A%E3%81%A8%E3%81%97%E3%81%A6%E9%9D%92%E3%81%84_stroke_%E3%82%92%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"context-stroke_を使用する","title":"<code>context-stroke</code>&nbsp;を使用する","isH3":false,"content":"<p>非標準かつ機能が制限された<code>context-stroke</code> (および<code>context-fill</code>) については <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/-moz-context-properties\"><code>-moz-context-properties</code></a> プロパティを参照して下さい。</p>","titleAsText":"context-stroke を使用する"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"要素","title":"要素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下の要素で<code>stroke</code>属性を使用できます。</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>&lt;shape&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>&lt;TextContent&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"使用可能な場所","id":"使用可能な場所"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"<code>context-stroke</code>&nbsp;を使用する","id":"context-stroke_を使用する"},{"text":"要素","id":"要素"}],"summary":"« SVG Attribute reference home","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"stroke","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"stroke","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"stroke","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"stroke","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"stroke","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/svg/attribute/stroke","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/svg/attribute/stroke/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG: スケーラブルベクターグラフィック"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性リファレンス"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stroke","title":"stroke"}],"pageTitl